quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  18,75,"(Khidr) jwatite: “Ana nganinansalila yanti chisimu mmwejo nganim’ba nkombwele kupilila none?”"
  18,76,"(Musa) jwatite: “Naga nam’busye yachindu chine panyuma pachalakwechi, basi ngasimungunda soni kulongana namwe, pamasile pampochele usulu wakwanila kuumila kukwangu.”"
  18,77,"Basi ni ŵajendelechele ŵanaŵaŵili (pa ulendo wao), mpaka pandema jaŵaichilile ŵandu ŵa m’musi (wa Antwâkia), ŵaŵendile yakulya achimisyene musio, nambo ŵakanile kwakalibuchisya. Basi ni ŵalisimene mwalakwemo lipupa linankusaka kugwa, basi (Khidr) ni jwalijimiche. (Musa) jwatite: “Nkasache, chisimu chene nkagapochelele malipilo (masengo galakwega nitukaasuumiile yakulya).”"
  18,78,"(Khidr) jwatite: “Aku ni kulekangana kwa chilikati cha une nomwe. Sano chinantagulile ngopolelo sya ichindu yanganinkombola kuipililila ata panandi.”"
  18,79,"“Sano chombochila, basi chaliji chaŵandu ŵakulaga ŵakamula masengo m’mbwani, ninasachile kuti nachipe ayibu, sano paujo pao paliji pana mwenye juŵaliji nkujigala chombo chilichose (chambone) mwakotosya.”"
  18,80,"“Sano kanchanda kala, nikuti achinangolo ŵakwe ŵaliji ŵakulupilila, basi nitwajogwepe kuti atakwakanganichisya kutenda yakusumba mpika ni yaukafili.”"
  18,81,“Nitwasachile kuti Ambuje ŵao ŵatindanichisye ni jwambone kumpunda jwele pakutakata ni jwakuŵandichila nnope ku chanasa (chakwatendela achinangolo ŵakwe).”
  18,82,"“Sano lipupa lila, nilyaliji lya ŵanache ŵaŵili ŵawina mu nsindamo; sano pasi pakwe paliji pana chipanje chao (chaŵasalachisye malemu baba ŵao); sano baba ŵao ŵaliji ntenda ngoto. Basi Ambuje ŵenu niŵasachile kuti akuyiche ŵanaŵaŵilio komangala kwao, mwanti chalikopochesye chipanje chaocho, (awu) kuŵa ukoto wakuumila kwa Ambuje ŵenu. Ni nganindenda yalakweyi mwaulamusi ŵangu. Asi ni ngopolelo sya ichindu yanganinkombola kuipililila.”"
  18,83,"Soni akum’busya (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) ya Dhul-Qarnain. Jilani: “Tinansoomele sine mwa abali syakwe.”"
  18,84,"Chisimu Uwwe twampele machili gakutamila pa chilambo, ni twampele soni litala lyakutendela chilichose"
  18,85,Ni jwakuyiye litala (lyakulungama ku ilambo yakwigulo)
  18,86,"Mpaka pajwaiche pakutiŵilila lyuŵa (mukalole kameso), ŵalisimene linankutiŵila petanda lyamatope gamapiliu, ni ŵasimene palakwepo ŵandu (makafili). Twatite: “E mmwe a Dhul- Qarnain! Naga nkusaka komboleka kwapa ilagasyo kapena kwatendela yambone.”"
  18,87,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Sano jwatesile lupuso (pakun’galagatila jwinepe jwangaŵaga Allah), basi chitumpe ilagasyo, kaneko tachiuchisyidwa kwa Ambujegwe, ni tachija kunnagasya ni ilagasyo yakunyalaya kusyene.”"
  18,88,"“Nambo jwaakulupilile ni kutendaga yambone, nikuti akwete kupata jwalakwejo malipilo gambone, soni chitunsalile yakwepepala mu ichindu yetu (yakun’jongolela).”"
  18,89,Kaneka jwakuyiye soni litala (lyakulungama ku ilambo yakundaŵi)
  18,90,"Mpaka pajwaiche pakopochela lyuŵa (mukalole kameso), ŵalisimene linankwakopochela ŵandu ŵanganitwaŵichila chakwasiŵilila ku lyalakwelyo"
  18,91,"Mwele nimuyaŵelele, chisimu soni Uwwe twaisyungwile yosope yayaliji kukwakwe (Dhul-Qarnain) paaimanya chenene"
  18,92,Kaneko jwakuyiye soni litala (line)
  18,93,"Mpaka pajwaiche chilikati chamatumbi gaŵili, ŵasimene chamungulugulu mwakwemo ŵandu ŵakuchelewa kupikana chiŵecheto"
  18,94,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “E mmwe a Dhul-Qarnain! Chisimu Yaajuju ni Maajuju akuwatanganya pa chilambo. Ana ngakomboleka kuti tumpe malipilo kuti m’biiche chilikati chetuwe ni ŵanganyao chakusiŵilila?”"
  18,95,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Ichindu yangombolasyisye une Ambuje ŵangu, iŵele yambone nnope (kupunda yankusaka kumbayo), basi mungamuchisyani mwamachili, timbiche chilikati chenu ni ŵanganyao chakusiŵilila chakulimbangana.”"
  18,96,"“Mumbani ipande ya isyano.” Mpaka pandema jajwagumbesye mpata wa matumbi gaŵiligo (ni isyanoyo), jwatite: “Pepelelani (moto).” Kwikanila ndema jajwaitesile (isyanoyo kuŵa yechejeu mpela) moto, jwatite: “Mumbani ntofu wenyelenyenduche naupungulile pachanya pakwe.”"
  18,97,"Basi (Yaajuju ni Maajuju) nganakombola kwela pachanya pakwe, nambo soni nganakombola kuchipowola"
  18,98,"(Dhul-Qarnain) jwatite: “Awu ni ukoto wakuumila kwa Ambuje ŵangu. Basi pachichiika chilangacha Ambuje ŵangu (chakopochela Yaajuju ni Maajuju Kiyama jili jisigele panandi), tachichitenda (chakusiŵililachi) kuŵa chakusyajidwa. Sano chilanga cha Ambuje ŵangu chiŵele chakuonaonape.”"